---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Programs
description: Explore the Deater Foundation programs that deliver rapid relief and long-term family resilience.
---
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary-600">Programs</p>
      <h1 class="section-heading mt-4">Comprehensive support for families on the edge</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600">Every program is shaped with input from caregivers, advocates, and community partners. Together we eliminate barriers that stand between families and stability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      {% for program in collections.programs %}
        <article class="flex flex-col rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/70 p-8 shadow-card">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900"><a class="hover:text-primary-600" href="{{ program.url }}">{{ program.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">{{ program.data.summary }}</p>
          <a class="btn-secondary mt-8 w-fit" href="{{ program.url }}">Learn more</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
